<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Super Admin Account Setup</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0;
        }
        .content {
            background: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 0 0 10px 10px;
        }
        .button {
            display: block; /* Make the button take full width for prominence */
            width: 80%; /* Adjusted width for better centering */
            max-width: 300px;
            background: #667eea;
            color: white !important; /* !important for email client compatibility */
            padding: 15px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px auto; /* Center the button */
        }
        .security-notice {
            background: #e3f2fd;
            border-left: 4px solid #2196f3;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .expiry-notice {
            background: #fff8e1;
            border-left: 4px solid #ffc107;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        /* Style for the school name to stand out */
        .school-name {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #764ba2;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>Welcome to Open School Portal!</h1>
        <p>Your Super Admin Account Setup is almost Ready</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
        <h2>Hello {{ superAdminName }},</h2>
        
        <p>To complete the initial setup and secure your account, please click the link below to create your Super Admin password:</p>
        
        <div style="text-align: center;">
            <a href="{{ setupLink }}" class="button">
                Set Your Password
            </a>
        </div>
        
        <p>Your Super Admin username is: <strong>{{ superAdminEmail }}</strong></p>
        
        <div class="expiry-notice">
            <strong>⚠️ Important:</strong> For security reasons, this setup link is only valid until <strong>{{ setupTokenExpiry }}</strong>. Please complete your setup before then.
        </div>
        
        <p>Once your password is set, you can log in and begin setting up your school configurations.</p>
        
        <div class="security-notice">
            <strong>Security Tip:</strong> Only click the link if you initiated this setup. If you have any concerns, please contact support.
        </div>
        
        <p>We're excited to have you on board! Need help? Contact our support team at support@osp.com</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
        <p>&copy; {{ currentYear }} Open School Portal. All rights reserved.</p>
        <p>This is an automated message, please do not reply to this email.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>